<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-30-0948 </DOCNO><TEXT>FMS-11/RSX V2.0 is a forms-oriented video I/O management system that iswell suited for use in traditional data entry applications. A recentattempt to use FMS-11 in a real-time process control application exposedseveral deficiencies. This paper describes modifications and additionsto FMS-11 required by the application, such as video attribute control,&quot;read-with-timeout,&quot; and programmable default menu responses. Some discussionis presented on the techniques used to approach this type of problem.</TEXT></DOC>